       The  ground  feature of each pixel by remote sensing data is calculated
       using rvi regression model.  After  run  r.rational.regression,  a  rvi
       model is a coefficient vector with the definition of:



                                 a[0]x1 + a[1]x2 + a[2]x3 + a[6]
               ground feature = ---------------------------------
                                 a[3]x1 + a[4]x2 + a[5]x3 + 1.0


